        "text": "greater damnation",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "] “pei taken longe dom,” Wyclif. The word denotes “judgment,” “punishment.” The verb from which it comes denotes “to judge,” pass sentence, condemn. In ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
